    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been reliably maintained. The exterior still has a great luster, though there are some minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small scratch on the rear passenger door. Inside, the cabin is clean and all electronics are fully functional, with only light wear on the driver's seat bolster. It drives smoothly and represents a solid, well-cared-for choice for its next owner.",
